              <a href="">Twitter</a>
              <a href="">Instagram</a>
          </ul>

          <ul>
              <p>Make Money with Us</p>
              <a href="">Sell on KTyres</a>
              <a href="">Sell under KTyres Accelerator</a>
              <a href="">Protect and Build Your Brand</a>
              <a href="">KTyres Global Selling</a>
              <a href="">Become an Affiliate</a>
              <a href="">KTyres Global Selling</a>
              <a href="">Advertise Your Products</a>
              <a href="">KTyres Pay on Merchants</a>
          </ul>

          <ul>
              <p> Let Us Help You</p>
              <a href="">COVID-19 and Amazon</a>
              <a href="">Your Account</a>
              <a href="">Returns Centre</a>
              <a href="">100% Purchase Protection</a>
              <a href="">KTyres App Download</a>
              <a href="">Help</a>
          </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="panel3">
          <div class="logo_img">

          </div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel4">
          <div class="pages">
              <a href="">Conditions of Use & Sale</a>
              <a href="">Privacy Notice</a>
              <a href="">Interest-Based Ads</a>
          </div>
          <div class="copyright">
              Â© 1996-2024, KTyres.com, Inc. or its affiliates
          </div>
      </div>

  </footer>
  </body>
</html>
